observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor require the Municipal Disaster and Risk Reduction Management Officer to prepare the:
• Summary/List of Donations Received, Distributed and Balances for In-kind Donations;
• Report on the Receipt and Utilization of Cash Donations;
• Report on the Receipts and Distribution/Issuance of Donated Relief Goods; and
• Report on the Receipts and Distribution/Issuance of Donated PPE and furnish the same to the NDRRMC, through the OCD, copy furnished the Audit Team within ten working days after the end of each quarter pursuant to COA Circular Nos. 2014-002 and 2020-009.
